    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape! It runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or fun weekend trips. It\u2019s clean, comfy, and honestly just a joy to drive. Come take it for a spin\u2014I know you're going to love it as much as I have!",
