    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Experience the raw performance of the LS7 7.0L V8, featuring a dry-sump lubrication system and titanium intake valves for high-RPM reliability. This Z06 utilizes a hydroformed aluminum chassis and carbon-fiber composite components to optimize the power-to-weight ratio. The Tremec 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp gate engagement, feeding power through a limited-slip differential. The FE4 performance suspension provides exceptional turn-in and lateral stability. Well-maintained with recent valve guide inspection and fluid service; minor aesthetic wear present, but the drivetrain is mechanically robust and track-ready.",
