    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven reliability. This specimen has been maintained to exacting standards, ensuring a seamless integration of performance and comfort. It exhibits a well-preserved aesthetic and mechanical soundness that commands confidence on every journey. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a refined driving experience that adheres to our dealership's rigorous criteria for quality and safety.",
