    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in really solid shape and ready for its next adventure! It runs like a dream and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got that perfect mix of being well-cared-for while still being ready for daily use. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to be a total steal! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat and would love to see this go to a great new home!",
