    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit boasts precise throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and has undergone a recent comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing service. Power is delivered to the rear wheels through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and an M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a vital preventative measure for this platform. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering and balanced handling characteristic of the M-division. While the paint shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain is robust and the VANOS system is fully serviced. A driver-grade icon for the serious enthusiast.",
